channel.title: What's going on?!
channel.description:
Okay, well I got a list of NPC spawns (Full RS list) and I added it to my autospawn, well now it takes forever (Almost an hour) to log my guy in. What it is doing basically is freezing my whole computer, yet when there is one or two or even 100 it loads instant? Is there a limit?
Base: DeltaCleaned.
